#. Tag: title
#: man-kmouth.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmouth.1.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmouth; is an application that enables persons that cannot speak to let "
"their computers speak. It includes a history of spoken sentences from which "
"the user can select sentences to be re-spoken."
msgstr ""
"&kmouth; je aplikacija, ki osebam, ki ne morejo govoriti, omogoča, da "
"pustijo svojim računalnikom govoriti. Vključuje zgodovino izgovorjenih "
"stavkov, iz katere lahko uporabnik izbere stavke, ki jih bo ponovno "
"izgovoril."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kmouth.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that &kmouth; does not include speech synthesizer. Instead it requires "
"a speech synthesizer installed in the system."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da &kmouth; ne vključuje sintetizatorja govora. Namesto tega "
"potrebuje sintetizator govora, nameščen v sistemu."

